{"tid":1469512,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"搞次機場道歉行動有冇得諗","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:19:53.000Z","uid":281784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"609a6d99d588bb0d52baab6d1f0c7b1fe04441cb","tid":1469512,"uid":281784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:04:44.000Z","msg":"唉 我到知大家都覺得尋日行動 <br />\n<br />\n由和你飛 變症 左你飛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我點都唔撚會割席 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而大家諗點補救 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n建議搞次 好似稅局 道歉行動 同埋變身左愛心 大使 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為旅客服務 教佢點答車 比水小食 佢地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家有冇得諗？<br />\n<br />\n希望有文宣巴絲幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4347f87744c5bc687219ec861638e7eb7f29d5a","tid":1469512,"uid":195998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"886ecc39857678a10e9e7568213bff8c8ca5d378","tid":1469512,"uid":274816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:19:53.000Z","msg":"有鬼還有鬼, 依家打輿論戰。<br />\n點都唔割蓆 同 道歉係 可以並行嘅<br />\n同稅務局個次一樣, 可以扳回一城之餘<br />\n和理非再發揮作用同勇武團結番大家<br />\n重點係今次事件正正就顯示, 機場係正苦最驚, 最難處理的兵家必爭之地, 出曬鬼都要搵辦法瓦解你!<br />\n和理非出黎道歉正正就令正苦冇藉口阻止到你<br />\n如果道歉都拉人, 輿論就會再次轉向"}]}